{"id": "1380510505223061624", "channel_id": "1380510505223061624", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "守密人你好：\n       彌薩格大學校務處將於6月6日19:35進行校內設施修復，更新完成後您將得到通知，重新進入遊戲。對於更新可能給大家帶來的不便，我們會準備一份補給物資以示歉意。祝大家調查順利！ \n  \n【補給物資】\n在線維護補償：銀芯*50\n  \n【領取條件】\n領取時間截至2025年6月20日23:59。請記得及時前往郵箱領取補給物資哦。  \n \n【更新內容】\n一、活動時間延長\n● 「千幕遊記」、「未被忘卻的」喚醒活動時間延長至6月30日關閉。\n● 「縈回維度的追隨」活動時間延長至6月23日關閉。\n● 「願希望再度萌芽」活動時間延長至7月14日關閉。\n● 「未被忘卻的」、「縈回維度的追隨」中領取幻衣繪形券的限時任務不做時間延長處理，新增任務結束倒計時顯示，結束時間為原活動結束時間（6月9日）。\n \n二、問題修復\n● 修復了戈利亞「狂氣爆發」確認按鈕未被翻譯的問題。\n● 調整了「序章」中前輩「瑪麗」和「六翼塔薇」的生命。\n● 修復了喚醒體「尤烏哈希」的靈塑適性在玩家生命低於 25％ 時，每次損失生命都會提高 1 次基礎傷害的問題。\n● 修復了喚醒體「卡斯托爾」超限爆發打出「黑羽」後施加「侵蝕」效果能夠被卡斯托爾的其他傷害技能觸發的問題。\n● 修復了「鏡像囚徒：飛躍青空」的「孤獨之旅」關卡獎勵「數理之書」未能正確享受到調查獎勵加成的問題。\n● 修復了「鏡像囚徒：飛躍青空」的「孤獨之旅」關卡獎勵掉落預覽錯誤的問題。", "timestamp": "2025-06-06T11:35:53.090000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1380510505474457600", "filename": "lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 131424, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1380510505223061624/1380510505474457600/lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg?ex=69cc5a59&is=69cb08d9&hm=f7258c670f8b6ab5bb5278b6a070456aaa1725c2e04840439f41f404aad857b0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1380510505223061624", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.2.2.6 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1380510658205843546", "channel_id": "1380510505223061624", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "V2.2.2.6 Online Maintenance Notice\n\nDear Keeper,\n    The Mythag University Administration Office will conduct facility repairs on June 6 at 19:35(UTC+8). You will be notified once the update is complete and can re-enter the game. We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause and will provide a supply package as compensation. Happy investigating!\n    \n【Supply Package】\nMaintenance Compensation: Silver*50\n    \n【Claim Conditions】\nClaim period ends on June 20 2025(UTC+8), at 23:59. Please remember to check your mailbox to claim the supply package.\n     \n【Update Content】\nI.Activity Duration Extension\n● The \"Kaleido Recollections\" and \"The Unforgotten\" Awakening Event durations have been extended until June 30. \n● The \"Guided Through Dimensions\" activity duration has been extended until June 23. \n● The \"May Hope Blossom Anew\" activity duration has been extended until July 14. \n● The time-limited tasks for receiving Skin Vouchers in \"The Unforgotten\" and \"Guided Through Dimensions\" will not have their durations extended. New task countdown displays have been added, with the end time set to the original event end time (June 9). \n \nII.Issue Fixes\n● Fixed an issue where the confirmation button for Goliath's \"Exalt\" was not translated. \n● Adjusted the HP of \"Mary\" and \"Six-Winged Tawil\" in the \"Prologue.\" \n● Fixed an issue where the Awakener \"Uvhash\" Soulforge Aptitude would increase base DMG by 1 every time HP dropped below 25%. \n● Fixed an issue where after \"Castor\" used Over-Exaltation to play \"Onyx Plume,\" the \"Corrosion\" effect could be triggered by Castor's other damage skills. \n● Fixed an issue where the \"Mathematics Textbook\" reward from the \"Solitude Journey\" level in \"Mirrored Prisoner: Soaring Blue Skies\" did not properly benefit from Investigation Reward buffs. \n● Fixed an issue with incorrect Drop Preview display for the \"Solitude Journey\" level reward in \"Mirrored Prisoner: Soaring Blue Skies.\"", "timestamp": "2025-06-06T11:36:29.564000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1380510505223061624", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.2.2.6 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
