{"id": "1380355668262916146", "channel_id": "1380355668262916146", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "守密人，\n    非常抱歉，自6月6日01:30（UTC+8）起，由於伺服器網路波動，導致部分守密人無法登入遊戲。\n    該問題現已修復，但由於緩存刷新較慢，部分守密人可能受到持續影響。若您目前仍無法登錄，請嘗試更換網路環境，並重新登入。\n\n\n【補給物資】\n網路波動補償：銀芯*1000\n  \n【領取條件】\n領取時間截至2025年6月20日23:59。請記得及時前往郵箱領取補給物資哦。", "timestamp": "2025-06-06T01:20:37.082000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1380355668652855366", "filename": "FB_IMG_1745246774005.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 57238, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1380355668262916146/1380355668652855366/FB_IMG_1745246774005.jpg?ex=69cc72e5&is=69cb2165&hm=f5f188c4652e5c6fd817ae0d142d60aab08bdd294c497b68c515ebcbfb168b26&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1380355668262916146", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "伺服器網路波動公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881"}
